    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Stem</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Water extract</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Can induce the replication of latent HIV-1infected U1cells in vitro, through NF-κB activation</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">[
     <xref rid="cit0025" ref-type="bibr">25</xref>]
    </td>
