     <italic>Sambucus nigra</italic> L.)
    </td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Caprifoliaceae</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Berries</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">96% ethanol purified fractions obtained from 50% ethanol, and water extracts</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Showed potent dose-dependent complement fixating activity and macrophage stimulating activity,
     <break/>might be responsible for the claimed effect of berry extracts on cold and influenza,
    </td>
