    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">23</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Red marine alga 
     <italic>Osmundaria obtusiloba</italic> (C. Agardh) R. E. Norris
    </td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Rhodomelaceae</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1"/>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Acetone extract</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Demonstrated that both fractions had potent inhibitory activity against HSV-1 (herpes simplex virus type 1) and present low toxicity for cell cultures</td>
