    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Whole plant</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Aqueous extract</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Had lowest anti-Herpes effect that at two hour was similar antiviral property of 
     <italic>Camellia sinensis</italic> at three hour.
    </td>
