     <italic>Phyllanthus watsonii</italic>
    </td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Phyllanthus</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Whole plant</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Aqueous extracts</td>
    <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">The first study that reported the antiviral activity against herpes simplex virus type-1 (HSV-1) and HSV-2 in Vero cells</td>
